      "description": "<p><strong>Max Ranks</strong>: 5</p><hr /><ul><li><p>A <strong>Charmed</strong> creature is partially infatuated with a particular target.</p></li><li><p>A <strong>Charmed</strong> creature increases its attitude to you, by 1 rank, for each rank of Charmed it has.</p></li><li><p>A <strong>Charmed</strong> creatures suffers a -2 penalty to Intelligence &amp; Wisdom based skill checks made against its infatuation for each rank it has.</p></li><li><p>A <strong>Charmed</strong> creature cannot take hostile actions towards the source of its infatuations. If they would suffer a hostile effect or damage from the source of its infatuations or one of its infatuations allies, they remove all ranks of this condition.</p></li></ul>",
